        <h1>Program</h1>
        <p>
          Terus berproses dan berprogres, Jangan banyak protes<br />
          Lakukan sampai beres
        </p>
        <div class="swiper program-slide">
          <div class="swiper-wrapper">
            <div class="swiper-slide">
              <div class="layout-slide">
                <span>Tahsin Ranger</span>
                <span>Al-Matsurat</span>
